snippet.title: Town Keeper Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Gameplay trailer for Town Keeper

Town Keeper is game about rebuilding rabbit town from fluffy empire's over run. 

Game Features:
- Tile-based town building focused on maximizing resource yields
- Train an army of fluffy defenders to protect your town
- Manage town resources, upgrades, trade, and research
- Flexible difficulty options from cozy to intense gameplay
- Unique towns to unlock and play. New townhalls, perks, and rabbit characters to discover.
- Cute bunny!!! Oh yea!!!

Get Town Keeper on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/3104510/Town_Keeper/
